OL,3,CDisabled traveller left 'housebound'
OL,4,Cafter wheelchair damaged on flight
OL,6,FWinter, who was diagnosed with Ehlers-
OL,7,FDanlos syndromes (EDS) and
OL,8,FFibromyalgia in 2009, which means they
OL,9,Fcannot walk more than a few feet
OL,10,Fwithout being in pain, contacted the
OL,11,Fwheelchair manufacturer, EZ Lite
OL,12,FCruiser, to evaluate the damage.
OL,14,FTheir report, concluded the chair had
OL,15,Fsuffered "serious damage to the frame"
OL,16,Fand "we recommend the device is
OL,17,Freplaced as it not safe to use in the
OL,18,Fcurrent condition".
