OL,3,CDisabled traveller left 'housebound'
OL,4,Cafter wheelchair damaged on flight
OL,6,FAer Lingus, who has since apologised,
OL,7,Finitially refused to offer Winter
OL,8,Fcompensation because the damage was
OL,9,Fnot reported at the time of arrival or
OL,10,Fwithin seven days.
OL,12,FNow, four months later, the airline
OL,13,Fhas agreed to cover the cost of a new
OL,14,Fchair but will not offer any further
OL,15,Fcompensation.
