OL,3,CDisabled traveller left 'housebound'
OL,4,Cafter wheelchair damaged on flight
OL,6,FWinter, who is due to start a Masters
OL,7,Fat the University of Liverpool in
OL,8,FSeptember, has spent months afraid to
OL,9,Fuse the damaged chair for fear it
OL,10,Fwould collapse, only leaving the house
OL,11,Fa handful of times when necessary.
OL,13,FWinter said that living without a
OL,14,Fchair has decimated their savings due
OL,15,Fto additional costs, such as having to
OL,16,Fpay for food deliveries and Ubers to
OL,17,Fget around.
